<table border=0 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=1>
	<tr>
		<td valign=middle align=left width=22><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=1 width=20 border=0></td>
		<td valign=middle align=right class="header">Managing Folders</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2"><hr size="1"></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Folders can be created to manage contacts efficiently.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Create New folder</td></tr>
    <tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">To create a new folder, click on the <strong>New Folder</strong> button. See Help on Creating New Folder</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Move Folder</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">A folder can be moved from within a folder to another.</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To move a folder, put a tick in checkbox at selected folder.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select the target folder to move to from the <strong>Folder</strong> list.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Move</strong> button to move the folder together with the contacts within, to the targetted folder.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Delete Folder</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To delete an existing folder, put a tick in checkbox at selected folder(s).</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Delete</strong> button. A confirmation pop-up message will appear before folders is deleted. Click on the <strong>OK</strong> button to delete or the <strong>Cancel</strong> button to cancel.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Caution: Deleting a folder will cause all the subfolders and contacts within to be deleted as well.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Send Message</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To send a message to all contacts in the folder, put a tick in checkbox at selected folder.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Send Message</strong> button. It will direct you to the <strong>Compose Message</strong> page with all the e-mail addresses of the contacts in the <strong>To</strong> field.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
